---
title: Crispy Breaded Tilapia with Asparagus, Lemon Chive Sauce, and Ciabatta Toasts
description: The beautiful thing about fish is that it rarely takes long to make—you can cook fillets on the stove and have them ready in a jiff. And that exactly what’s happening here: tilapia is coated in a crispy panko crust and pan-fried to a beautiful golden brown. Add some asparagus on the side and a few buttered ciabatta toasts and presto! You’ve got one seriously tasty catch of the day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-breaded-tilapia-719d6b8e.jpg
